Package: fuzzysys
Type: Package
Title: Simple Fuzzy Inference and Fuzzy Systems
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Patricia", "Angkiriwang", email="p.angkiriwang@oceans.ubc.ca",
    role=c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Useful tools to build a simple fuzzy rule-based expert system model.
    Highly customizable for a variety of needs, without the clutter. A re-imagining of the fuzzy set and inference functions from the package `sets`, with more customizability and control.
